{"tid":1560683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對要脅 只得一個方法","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T10:04:30.000Z","uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20907d2650aeff048658abc03f4381f8c40637a6","tid":1560683,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">增加曝光率 </span>搵議員、傳媒、使館之類 一定要有咁大搞咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要用盡一切方法留低證據 交比除親人外信得過嘅人<br />\n我講緊嘅唔淨止關乎肇事者 而係所有間接嘅知情人士都一樣 即使目前仲未受到威脅 都要有以上準備<br />\n<br />\n事實上你被要脅果一刻 就已經等於死咗 包括你屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論你幾乖幾聽話 中共事後一定會清算你地 因為死人最能保守秘密 依樣大家都應該好清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n風聲過後 你嘅價值就會隨之而失去 <br />\n更容易落手 到時先爆料都無用了"},{"pid":"a7d6fc719ee0412a8c83d8298566d0f6fce7998d","tid":1560683,"uid":258592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"依家個環境有幾咁黑暗大家都好清楚<br />\n<br />\n我想表達嘅就係 我地每一個人都唔應該心存僥倖<br />\n覺得你唔會關事 因為中共殺錯人都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aed51b11a8a34018be439a891eefcb85ab9f36","tid":1560683,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k